{"tha-ap59:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap59:0.2":"Bijanivagga ","tha-ap59:0.3":"Pancadipakattheraapadana ","tha-ap59:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap59:1.2":"sabbabhutanukampino; ","tha-ap59:1.3":"Saddahitvana saddhamme, ","tha-ap59:1.4":"ujuditthi ahosaham. ","tha-ap59:2.1":"Padipadanam padasim, ","tha-ap59:2.2":"parivaretvana bodhiyam; ","tha-ap59:2.3":"Saddahanto padipani, ","tha-ap59:2.4":"akarim tavade aham. ","tha-ap59:3.1":"Yam yam yonupapajjami, ","tha-ap59:3.2":"devattam atha manusam; ","tha-ap59:3.3":"Akase ukkam dharenti, ","tha-ap59:3.4":"dipadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap59:4.1":"Tirokuttam tiroselam, ","tha-ap59:4.2":"samatiggayha pabbatam; ","tha-ap59:4.3":"Samanta yojanasatam, ","tha-ap59:4.4":"dassanam anubhomaham. ","tha-ap59:5.1":"Tena kammavasesena, ","tha-ap59:5.2":"pattomhi asavakkhayam; ","tha-ap59:5.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap59:5.4":"dvipadindassa sasane. ","tha-ap59:6.1":"Catuttimse kappasate, ","tha-ap59:6.2":"satacakkhusanamaka; ","tha-ap59:6.3":"Rajahesum mahateja, ","tha-ap59:6.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap59:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap59:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap59:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap59:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pancadipako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap59:9.1":"Pancadipakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}